articles.title: Gift to Kim Jong Il from Cuban Organization
articles.content:
Gift to Kim Jong Il from Cuban Organization

					Pyongyang, September 26 (KCNA) -- Leader Kim Jong Il received a gift from the Cuban Institute of Friendship with the Peoples.
					
					The gift was handed to an official concerned on Monday by the President of the Institute Kenia Serrano Puig.

articles.title: Yang Hyong Sop Meets Cuban Guests
articles.content:
Yang Hyong Sop Meets Cuban Guests

					Pyongyang, September 26 (KCNA) -- Yang Hyong Sop, vice-president of the Presidium of the Supreme People's Assembly of the DPRK, met and had a friendly talk with Kenia Serrano Puig, president of the Cuban Institute of Friendship with the Peoples, and her party at the Mansudae Assembly Hall Monday.

articles.title: DPRK Premier Leaves for China
articles.content:
DPRK Premier Leaves for China

					Pyongyang, September 26 (KCNA) -- Premier of the DPRK Cabinet Choe Yong Rim, member of the Presidium of the Political Bureau of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea, left here on Monday to pay an official goodwill visit to China at the invitation of Premier of the State Council of China Wen Jiabao, member of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China.
